description: My family and I went on a long-awaited vacation. It was three rainy days. I went for a walk alone, looked at the sea for a long time and walked along the shore. It started raining heavily and I ran to the hotel, the rain was getting stronger, I looked at a bush with flowers and thought: today is November, flowers in November are a miracle for a northern person. I took the flower with one hand and took a picture with the other hand. A drop of rain fell on the picture.
